<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="such-as">such as</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>诸如；例如：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cartoon characters such as Mickey Mouse and Snoopy are still popular.
像米老鼠和史努比这样的卡通人物仍然很受欢迎。</p></div>

<p>注: such as常用来进行列举，并直接放在列举的名 词之前。for example表示“例如”，用来举例说明某一情况或论点，可放在句首、句中或句末。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She does well in many subjects such as mathematics, physics, and chemistry.
她许多学科的成绩都很好，比如数学、物理和化学。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His spelling is terrible! For example, look at this word.
他的拼写太糟糕了，例如，就看看这个单词吧。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mexico, Canada, and China, for example, all have oil reserves.
例如墨西哥、加拿大和中国，都有石油储备。</p></div></div>